'''Thiss''' was an enormous fire-blackened stump of a [[Wroshyr tree/Legends|wroshyr tree]] on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] that acted as a landing field for nearby [[Rwookrrorro/Legends|Rwookrrorro]]. A monument to [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] was created here that was carved from the branch of a huge wroshyr tree and held a portrait of the Wookiee to honor his life as well as the contributions he made to the [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]].

